{"tid":890690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學生動源：香港學生必須知的香港歷史】","createTime":"2018-11-05T13:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T05:14:05.000Z","uid":153615,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf397e37e6a74975edcd66329b844c1a1f53964","tid":890690,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"【香港學生必須知的香港歷史】<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立進程已經塵封百年之久，本應早在獨立路途上邁向終點，卻被中共屢番阻撓，在上世紀七十年代停滯至今，而泛民主派當初所主張的《民主回歸論》亦令香港民族未來蒙上陰影。<br />\n<br />\n根據《南京條約》及《北京條約》香港島及九龍半島均為永久割讓予英國成為英國殖民地。因此香港島及九龍半島毋須歸還予原宗主國。<br />\n<br />\n新界則在清國根據《展拓香港界址專條》租借予英國九十九年，惟清國《清室退位詔書》中僅提及「仍合滿、漢、蒙、回、藏五族完全領土為一大中華民國」，當中並無提及任何因各種條約而租借、割讓之領土，而《清室退位詔書》亦無提及清國與外國條約的權利及義務之繼承，故此清繼承國中華民國並無繼承收回新界之權利，更遑論於1949年以武力奪取政權的中華人民共和國。<br />\n<br />\n另外根據聯合國大會第1514（15）號決議，香港原本與其他同樣於殖民地名單的地區擁有獨立自決的權利，然而中共在一九七二年於聯合國動議將香港和澳門剔除殖民地名單。令香港喪失獨立自決的機會，及後英國更與中共進行密室談判，將香港的獨立自決權體無完膚地剝削，香港人無法參與其中，被迫接受中國殖民。<br />\n<br />\n香港人一直都沒有當家作主的機會，昔日繁榮昌盛的東方之珠，在中共政權摧殘之下漸漸失去光芒，若然香港人繼續沉醉於一國兩制的謊言，香港將加快遭受中共徹底摧殘，完全淪為中國殖民地。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studentlocalism/photos/a.1034067780001639/1669136066494804/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudentlocalism%2Fphotos%2Fa.1034067780001639%2F1669136066494804%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=w5yGqUan81Y6HPaDGCH1WS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=54c2138f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/studentlocalism/photos/a.1034067780001639/1669136066494804/?type=3</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0PJm6mF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PJm6mF.png&h=ec58144b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffd400de7dbe5b67a86f2373c6ff9c2756ce6983","tid":890690,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cebbebf9b56f51493bffaffecd909d91daca6b9b","tid":890690,"uid":81113,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"另外post五毛退散圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ujUGWi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ujUGWi.png&h=d75ca86a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXgshuE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXgshuE.png&h=8390dce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vFs1Wj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vFs1Wj.png&h=103dc0ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc731cedb81f415d01d9be968cccac5e64bafc5b","tid":890690,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"好多post要推"},{"pid":"3f88b8bfb32c24fdab64c12b4809dbf39a0957c3","tid":890690,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc731cedb81f415d01d9be968cccac5e64bafc5b","tid":890690,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"好多post要推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:54:01.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdbee46c69790881ca6af8da456c5359a89d5aa","tid":890690,"uid":24133,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U7oencx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU7oencx.png&h=5fb138c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48e57a5919af6a6f45879420b4cb432af03105f9","tid":890690,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bdbee46c69790881ca6af8da456c5359a89d5aa","tid":890690,"uid":24133,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U7oencx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU7oencx.png&h=5fb138c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"竟有此事？！"},{"pid":"89c8f553682b898a51b1cbee9011998eea45e6b6","tid":890690,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"